          <title>Nvidia Faces Revenue Threat Amid U.S. Export Restrictions on AI Chips</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Nvidia faces significant revenue threat due to latest U.S. export restrictions on artificial intelligence chips, analysts and investors said on Monday. The regulations limit AI chip exports to most countries except for select group of close U.S. allies.]]></description>
